headline: Sempra Infrastructure Justin Bird Honored with the 2025 Lifetime Achievement GRIT Award
summary: Justin Bird, CEO of Sempra Infrastructure and Executive Vice President of Sempra, has dedicated over two decades to advancing energy infrastructure and corporate development, steering critical operations that have shaped the energy industry's future.

headline: ConocoPhillips Strikes 20-Year LNG Deal With Sempra's Port Arthur
summary: COP secures a 20-year deal to buy 4 MTPA of LNG from Sempra's Port Arthur Phase 2, expanding its global energy footprint.
